!!【柯林斯英汉双解大词典】

:<div>

research /rɪˈsɜːtʃ, ˈriːsɜːtʃ/

(researching,researched,researches) 

1. N-UNCOUNT Research is work that involves studying something and trying to discover facts about it. 研究 [also N in pl] 

例： Sixty-five percent of the 1987 budget went for nuclear weapons research and production. 1987年预算的65%用在了核武器的研制上。 

2. V-T If you research something, you try to discover facts about it. 研究 

例： She spent two years in South Florida researching and filming her documentary. 她在南佛罗里达花了两年的时间研究和拍摄纪录片。 

3. researcher N-COUNT 研究员 

例： He chose to join the company as a market researcher. 他选择加入这家公司当一名市场研究员。

</div>

